; font_container=&#8221;tag:h4|text_align:center|color:%23545c79&#8243; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; cryptoland_ch_style=&#8221;normal&#8221; fliping_text=&#8221;&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1634025516507{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}&#8221; res_sm_mb=&#8221;0&#8243; cryptoland_vc_css_768=&#8221;.vc_custom_1634025516510{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}&#8221;][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Road Map&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h2|text_align:center&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; css_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; fliping_text=&#8221;&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1541311857087{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}&#8221; res_sm_mb=&#8221;35&#8243; cryptoland_vc_css_768=&#8221;.vc_custom_1541311857097{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}&#8221;][\/vc_column][vc_column res_sm_ml=&#8221;20&#8243;]<div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6 offset-lg-4 col-sm-8 offset-sm-4\"><div class=\"road road-2 \"><div class=\"road__item\"><div class=\"road__item-metka\"><\/div><div class=\"road__item-content\"><div class=\"road__item-title\">October 2021<\/div><p>The digital asset\/crypto exchange, which is part of the COREX ecosystem, is set to launch in October 2021. The exchange is characterized by favorable fee conditions, ease of use, system reliability, and speediness of the system.\n<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"road__item road__item-active\"><div class=\"road__item-metka\"><\/div><div class=\"road__item-content\"><div class=\"road__item-title\">October 2021<\/div><p>COREX blockchain public network will be fully functional starting October, making it possible to generate a variety of smart contracts in the blockchain. \n<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"road__item\"><div class=\"road__item-metka\"><\/div><div class=\"road__item-content\"><div class=\"road__item-title\">December, 2021<\/div><p>We will start to develop the first ever blockchain-based application, which is going to be the \u201cNational Loyalty System\u201d.\n<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"road__item\"><div class=\"road__item-metka\"><\/div><div class=\"road__item-content\"><div class=\"road__item-title\">January, 2022<\/div><p>COREX will offer additional services based on blockchain and cryptocurrencies for its exchange clients.\n<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"road__item\"><div class=\"road__item-metka\"><\/div><div class=\"road__item-content\"><div class=\"road__item-title\">Q1, 2022<\/div><p>NFT marketplace, which aims to enhance the value of Mongolian artists' work, and to create a financial solution for them to focus more on their work, will be introduced.\n<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"road__item\"><div class=\"road__item-metka\"><\/div><div class=\"road__item-content\"><div class=\"road__item-title\">Q1, 2022<\/div><p>The asset tokenization service that links conventional financial products to crypto economy will be introduced.\n<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"road__item\"><div class=\"road__item-metka\"><\/div><div class=\"road__item-content\"><div class=\"road__item-title\">Q2, 2022<\/div><p>Start to build up a blockchain community to develop and to broaden the usage of blockchain technology in Mongolia.\n<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"road__item\"><div class=\"road__item-metka\"><\/div><div class=\"road__item-content\"><div class=\"road__item-title\">Q3, 2022<\/div><p>The \u201cNational Loyalty System\u201d will be introduced to the public so that  companies and brands will be able to create their own tokens to reward their loyal customers and the exchange clients will be able to trade and buy the tokens.\n<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"road__item\"><div class=\"road__item-metka\"><\/div><div class=\"road__item-content\"><div class=\"road__item-title\">Q1, 2023<\/div><p>We will expand the utilization of COREX blockchain in the region and will list CRX coin on foreign exchanges.\n<\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row_content_no_spaces&#8221; cryptoland_row_overflow=&#8221;overflow_visibl